, confirmed that Nowicki received a subpoena and is coordinating with U.S. officials to possibly circumvent the need for his testimony before a grand jury.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maksymilian_Nowicki\", \"score\": 0.9785937858677991, \"rank\": 0.021874449577503632, \"text\": \"Nowicki\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maksymilian_Nowicki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maksymilian_Nowicki\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes in question reportedly tested positive for trimetazidine-a substance banned for its performance-enhancing effects-shortly before the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This substance is known to enhance endurance and has been prohibited by the World Anti-Doping Agency (WADA) since 2014.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1240, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Anti-Doping Agency (WADA)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read the full story \\u203a  You must belogged into post a comment.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"About us  Subscribe  Go Ad-Free  Privacy policy  Copyright \\u00a9 2025 WorldNetDaily  Copyright \\u00a9 2025 WorldNetDaily  December 5, 2025  WND Comics  December 5, 2025  Bob Unruh  December 5, 2025  WND Staff\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldNetDaily\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WND\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldNetDaily\", \"dbpedia